TorchTSNE provenance notice
===========================

This package is a high-performance implementation that mirrors and adapts parts of the
behavior and implementation strategy of scikit-learn's t-SNE stack for a
Torch/CUDA-oriented setting.

Upstream reference project:

- scikit-learn
- https://github.com/scikit-learn/scikit-learn
- https://scikit-learn.org/

Upstream license:

- BSD 3-Clause License

Attribution preserved here because the implementation includes logic best described
as a port or adaptation of scikit-learn behavior, validation rules, optimizer
schedule, and benchmarking comparisons rather than a fully clean-room,
independently invented implementation.
